Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是個布丁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在飯後享用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千真是孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個布丁一口氣吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可是特別的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千佳每當有新品種上市的時候都要研究配方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你現在吃了做研究不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有那麼一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那布丁是個什麼樣子的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芒果布丁和牛奶布丁各半
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有草莓啦菠蘿啦之類的水果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有賣海綿蛋糕的便利店看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩捉迷藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來扮鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒快去躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是相信你的喲  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會做那麼過分的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純地想玩捉迷藏吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你喲  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我至少也得在這裡守著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你給我慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是當真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真的想吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  找到小千了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還這麼相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭小美了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什麼好笑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太小看我了  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到或許會被抓現行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也買了個一樣的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你倒是吃了它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:07.26,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『無論何時。』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說過不要把菸灰缸放在奇怪的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上扔煙蒂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要被爸爸罵了 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「吸菸有害健康」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙盒上也這麼寫著的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上當了吧  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒給煙點上火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這丫頭～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓之cosplay再襲！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個是前幾天美羽給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉果然就是適合這種打扮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是有些難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別摘下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說茉莉  說聲「喵」來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說快說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好可愛  好適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:05:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本就扎雙辮兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些缺乏平衡感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個挺適合安娜的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  或許不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借來一用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  天衣無縫～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太合適了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就收下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還我！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子一寂寞就會死的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  小美會因此悲觀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  安娜的兔耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒在聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜  戴著那個果然很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  說這話的茉莉自己不也很可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後都會是強者取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德古拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家還真什麼都有嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的鮮血獻給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然年輕人的鮮血才是最美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有養顏潤膚的功效
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好髒的  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人腦子太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個就輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不成  是個老太太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你倒是吸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還只是個女大學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個  可惡的德古拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊  這裡有些畫歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這麼仔細…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這招
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又用洗衣機洗運動鞋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得洗手帕什麼的  你這樣弄得好不衛生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千你還洗過麵包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我最喜歡的那件襯衫滿是麵包屑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討…討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了好多次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小美自做主張放口袋裡去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小腳趾撞到桌腿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  小腳趾很疼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把注意力集中到新的疼痛上來  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸  吸  呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初一數學？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想和安娜練習英語的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能弄錯…茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好歹是個短大生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短大生  我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為姐姐也就這種學力嗎？嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可還什麼都沒做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是想  你會給我一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先躺著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  或許…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後去一趟書店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概能換的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的初一倒是教些挺難的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一本是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…你沒買錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪汪和咕嚕？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看著這場景我就心懷不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不安什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心茉莉今後能不能順順利利地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是能活下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的茉莉怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？和平常差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上從樓梯摔下來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國語課上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去撿掉地上的鉛筆然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭又撞上了桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡  眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳課時是一直跟在我邊上練習雙腳划水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換衣服也非常的慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後好像就不大舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以休息時間就在保健室睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休結束了還在吃學校提供的午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回家的時候又在鞋櫃前摔了個跟頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管這叫和平常差不多？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和平常差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是漫畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜也真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你聽了剛才這些還覺得茉莉沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  有些不安了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得現在使茉莉得到新生就是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我還擁有一頭烏黑的頭髮的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你頭髮不是茶色的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是茶色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我覺得沒有那麼容易根治
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始要讓茉莉獲得新生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉那滿臉幸福的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真安逸啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就到了追求安逸的年紀了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來讓你獲得安逸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒這本事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我這撫慰人心的pose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒覺得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  你是嫁不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像小千又上你的當了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某一天  雙胞胎的一對小狗汪汪和咕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他們玩耍的空地上找到了一個栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪把自己的耳朵貼近栗子去聽動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果什麼也聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕舔了栗子一口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有點鹹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在好大好大的樹的根部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又發現一個栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣汪就有一個  咕嚕也有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時佐竹登門來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像渡邊淳司一樣說到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這還真是個出色的栗子呢  請恕我失禮」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就喀嚓喀嚓地吃了栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得肚子脹得厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁著搖晃的步子地走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這書上根本沒寫這麼回事  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我騎摩托先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜  你今天是走來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐我車後面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得走河邊那條路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐兩個人很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那茉莉就坐我車後了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是騎車來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這書好像是買錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的英語會話\N中學一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即就讓換真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多虧姐姐在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸惠姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上班去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是家庭餐廳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那裡已經不讓她進了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有些口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們去家庭餐廳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（TV04話時伸惠打工所在的餐廳，全稱是「Family Restaurant」）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美  你帶錢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錢不就去不成家庭餐廳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？是麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上還帶了些錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有200日圓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AA制  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～是～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的夕陽真特別…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你這丫頭做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙  被什麼咬了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是別胡來了  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙用橡皮筋射你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回敬她一個  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣了  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可能有傷人的勇…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿毛巾來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想真下手的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來再來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  現在正是發洩長久以來的怨恨的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫因果報應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我這制裁的一記飛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nogueira
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你那膝蓋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用膝蓋非常漂亮地給了她脛骨上一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nogueira是使用關節技的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：Antonio Rodrigo Nogueira，巴西柔術高手，擅用關節技和倒地攻擊術）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳  絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋轉攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋轉攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉暈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽  你這樣很吵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  小美  撲到我懷裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？果然你是最喜歡我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千  我愛死你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受到了橡皮筋  膝蓋和牆造成的共計127點的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻還像你現在看到的一樣活力十足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,127點這麼多了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美你多長HP？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HP是個什麼玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你那數字是個什麼玩意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要增加HP
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不還是HP嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉的HP現在是2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？才只有2？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說這些也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到院子裡去  吃點樹木的果實啊落在地上的種子啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遊戲玩太多了  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏地挺身你做得了嗎  茉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰臥起坐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你先去一次醫院再回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼成了這麼亂糟糟的一片？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了鍛鍊茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令她即使失去了我們也能依靠自己活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說話聲音又細又小
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你大聲喊出來會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別教茉莉些奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧—！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…來吧—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招—！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀—！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早熟女—！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘰裡呱啦噼哩啪啦—！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘰裡呱啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉你不必真照做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要是大家都不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實光是少我一個的話  你似乎就不能在學校生活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能因此就突然讓人家自立啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:22:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是應該從外表上開始改變比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內在的東西似乎很花時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.79,0:23:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡而言之  就是能壓倒周圍的裝扮就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼先請團長說兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是弄的茉莉很無奈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同…同志們辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.19,0:25:31.20,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『每一天。』
